for the following dockerfile how big will the image be?

FROM scratch
copy ./5gbfile.txt .
(the file 5gbfile.txt has a size of 5 gb)

for the following dockerfile how big will the image be?

FROM scratch
copy ./5gbfile.txt .
run rm ./5gbfile.txt
(the rm command would not be avialable in this container because it starts from scratch but image that it is available)

